.about Exercise 25
.import ex_proj
.pragma main sqd
.pragma extended True

1 define: d1 [ ] compair diff pr_L pr_R
2 define: d2 [ ] compair diff pr_R pr_L
3 define: vabsdif [ ] compair add d1 d2
4 define: dupl [ ] pair id id
5 define: duplvabsdif [ ] comp dupl vabsdif
6 define: sqd [ ] comp mul duplvabsdif

===

diff pr_L pr_R es lo mismo que diff
diff pr_R pr_L es comp diff swap

vabsdif: comp add pair diff comp diff swap
sqd: comp mul comp dupl vabsdif

